author: glasser
msg: Fix depth tests 12 and 13 against svnserve 1.4.  If we're updating at
depth "unknown", and we receive a delete for an entry we don't know
about, but we're at depth empty or files, then just ignore it.
(delete_entry): Ignore deletes on things that we think are too deep

author: sussman
msg: Prepare libsvn_wc to invoke conflict-callback on property conflicts.
(This commit doesn't change any visible behaviors.)
(svn_wc_merge_props2):  rev this API, adding conflict callback.
apply_single_prop_change):  take conflict callback args, invoke new helper func.
(svn_wc__merge_props):  take conflict args, pass to apply* functions.
(merge_props):  take conflict callback args, pass to svn_wc__merge_props().
